        [
          "As a mortal you always knew you were related to a murderous group of killers, although you never had contact with them. Your sire formed The Spiral Sign of Sabbat who were part of these killers, then he has a prophecy that an Avatar of Caine will ascend the throne of Caine and as Regent of the Sabbat will lead the sect to victory against the Antediluveans. You and your pack are constantly searching for the right person, traits, rituals, or materials.  Most simply become regular vampires, others die in great agony.  None have turned into an Avatar of Caine yet, but it's only a matter of time.  Your sire Xerxes made you the Pack Priest once he entered Torpor and today he sends you visions of candidates to embrace, those marked with The Spiral Sign.  You fear for your Sire's safety in this warzone and want to leave to continue your hunt.  If you must fight it should be with the Black Spirals at your side or not at all."
